{"tid":1259244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NOW：郭榮鏗批梁美芬「奴隸」被逐出會議廳","createTime":"2019-06-26T13:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T14:28:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d32319f348ed3b485ff5f4b1801ddba867f83d7a","tid":1259244,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗在立法會大會上形容經民聯梁美芬是「奴隸」，立法會主席梁君彥裁定用字具冒犯性，郭榮鏗拒絕收回言論，被梁君彥逐出會議廳。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗拒絕收回言論，被立法會主席趕離會議廳，多名保安圍着他，泛民議員亦行近阻止保安把他抬走，郭榮鏗最終自行步出會議廳，是他自2012年出任立法會議員以來首次被逐出會議廳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1610277a543b6da45380afc2d5b7d7bab87b841a","tid":1259244,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"奴隸芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e11169fb1dc1ecb75656ad03db7f727e7c95d25","tid":1259244,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"共奴"},{"pid":"a713c0fb8e4eac8a6c352da740705b67cacf9714","tid":1259244,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"當時佢個表情應該係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWq2Od7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWq2Od7.jpg&h=4ba12053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3705ff143bc661411b2b018a0220890790dc2bcf","tid":1259244,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"遲奶! bu young 做奴隸 de 印抆<br />\n有咩問題"},{"pid":"6be66d03a0e21436330e47e49171b0cbe8cd8b90","tid":1259244,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"起來！不願做奴隸的人們"},{"pi